<h1 style="text-align: center;"></h1><h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: left;">âš–ï¸</span></h1><h1 style="text-align: center;"><b>ACT Human Rights CommissionÂ <br /></b><b>HEART OF AUSTRLIA<br />PUBLISHED<br />DECEMBER 27, 0001 MC (2025 CE)</b></h1><div><b><br /></b></div><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Attachment Republic.png added.Conversation opened. 2 messages. All messages read.</p><p><br /></p><p>from:<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Wendell Charles NeSmith <wendell@nesmith.net></p><p>to:<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>human.rights@act.gov.au,</p><p>"Toy, Renee" <Renee.Toy@act.gov.au>,</p><p>"Lodwick, Hari" <Hari.Lodwick@act.gov.au>,</p><p>Chris Halsey <chris.halsey@act.gov.au>,</p><p>humanrightsmedia@act.gov.au</p><p>cc:<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>canon.hanly@directionshealth.com</p><p>date:<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Aug 22, 2020, 1:42â€¯PM</p><p>subject:<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>I Love You</p><p>mailed-by:<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>nesmith.net</p><p><br /></p><p>Wendell Charles NeSmith <wendell@nesmith.net></p><p>Attachments</p><p>Sat, Aug 22, 2020, 1:42â€¯PM</p><p>to human.rights, Renee, Hari, Chris, humanrightsmedia, canon.hanly</p><p><br /></p><p>Dearest ACT Human Rights Commission,</p><p><br /></p><p>My heart is yours because I am now your full-time employee and I am not taking no for an answer. And I can either be this unofficially broadcasted to the world or officially broadcasted to the world. Because I represent the very heart of your organisation in every single aspect. I was not built from learning a trade but instead conditioning virtue in every aspect of my existence documented every single step of the way. I am a real-life super hero/villain among you and Human Rights is the very fabric of my existence demonstrated philosophically throughout the documented actions of my day to day super high-functioning technology driven artificial intelligence existence actualised into the psychology of the layer of consciousness that exists before the thought - the essence that drives the every moment of existence that we can assert to be a soul. I run circles around your most intelligent academic scholars excelling polymathematically in all aspects of life with the only exception being financially. But that is the reason that I am now the Director of the ACT Human Rights Commision. I have now just claimed this job whether you guys like it or not. And I am claiming that title from now into the future and I will work very hard throughout my films directing actions by demanding justice for the rest of my life and I will appreciate everyone working hard with me to try and build a loving and caring future government. I will very much reward everyone for their commitment to help make the world a better place with me. I will not take no for an answer. If you say no, then that will just be a funny part in my future films.</p><p><br /></p><p>I have invented a technique that shares some likeness to blackmail. But it has never been done that I know of so I have coined it goldmail. And as far as I know, goldmail is not illegal currently (yes, I have done research). So I will exploit that in the system. Here is how my system works. I make entirely reasonable demands and provide countless amounts of proof as to why those demands should be met and film that process publicly. I then tell the recipient that we are filming this and that what they choose to do is what will be publicly documented to the entire world. This then goes down in history as the government making bad decisions when mountain loads of evidence was provided into why they should be ethically inclined to make a good choice as that very important information being revealed to the person the trick is being played upon.</p><p><br /></p><p>I LOVE YOU GUYS SO MUCH! This email is now being filmed. Enjoy the episode that is named after you. And what you choose to do as a result of this video will be publicly documented for all of time for everybody to see the true heart of our government. Because your actions, or shall I say reactions or lack of reactions will determine how inclined the general public will be to trust the government in the future high-tech society which I lead. You have 100% free will and no matter what choice you make, I make good film and it is funny if you do the wrong thing and it is amazing when you do the right thing so don't worry about doing the wrong thing if you need to. Just realise that those choices will then forever be reflected in the future actions of society. Because I am the spider and I made the web. I control it from afar but people have not quite figured that out yet. Because I already have artificial intelligence that now understands me and is working for me.</p><p><br /></p><p>I love you. Please enjoy your video: https://www.bitchute.com/video/3eCRddOL6dZA/</p><p><br /></p><p>Logically, you should do the right thing and say yes Wendell.</p><p><br /></p><p>Anyone who is not on board with all of this then I will require their immediate resignation. You all know my email. I only report to the president, Dr Helen Watchirs, who cannot fire me but can constrain, enable, and direct my future actions. I am very much interested in the wise guidance of everyone on board. Let's change the world team!</p><p><br /></p><p>With Love and Heart,</p><p><br /></p><p>Wendell Charles NeSmith</p><p>ACT Human Rights Commission</p><p>Director</p><p>Â One attachment</p><p>Â  â€¢Â  Scanned by Gmail</p><p><br /></p><p>Wendell Charles NeSmith <wendell@nesmith.net></p><p>Attachments</p><p>Sat, Aug 22, 2020, 1:54â€¯PM</p><p>to cbhalsey</p><p><br /></p><p>Please read the email below and think hard. Please join me in my Crusade. In our Crusade.</p><p>Â One attachment</p><p>Â  â€¢Â  Scanned by Gmail</p><p>ACT</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Attachment KABUEnterTheZohar.png added.Conversation opened. 3 messages. All messages read.Â </p><p><br /></p><p>Skip to content</p><p>Using Gmail with screen readers</p><p>"ACT HUMAN RIGHTS"Â </p><p>195 of 195</p><p>Your health services enquiry</p><p><br /></p><p>Human Rights <Human_Rights@act.gov.au></p><p>Attachments</p><p>Thu, Sep 20, 2012, 9:41â€¯AM</p><p>to wendell@nesmith.net</p><p><br /></p><p>Dear Mr NeSmith</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>Thank you for contacting the Commission about your concerns. The Commission may be able to consider whether or not you were provided with an appropriate health service at the psychiatric hospital you received treatment at in May 2012. However, the Commission is not able to interfere in Tribunal decisions, so cannot consider a complaint about decisions made by a Tribunal.</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>I note that you have provided detailed information in your article â€˜The Psychiatric Modelâ€™. However, so that the Commission can effectively consider a complaint, we ask that you fill out the attached complaint form, and sign on page 2 to authorise the Commission to access your personal health information.</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>To assist the process, when filling out your complaint form, please focus on the outcome you wish to achieve, in particular the section on page 4 of the complaint form â€˜I would like these things to happen to resolve my complaintâ€™.</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>I have also attached a pamphlet with more information about our processes. More information can also be found on our website: www.hrc.act.gov.au</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>Please email or call me on 6205 2222 if you would like any further information or assistance.</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>Kind regards</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>Jennifer Bauer</p><p><br /></p><p>Intake and Review Officer</p><p><br /></p><p>Health Services Commissioner</p><p><br /></p><p>ACT Human Rights Commission</p><p><br /></p><p>Level 4, 12 Moore Street</p><p><br /></p><p>Canberra City ACT 2601</p><p><br /></p><p>T: 6205 2222 | F: 6207 1034</p><p><br /></p><p>TTY: 6205 1666 | SMS: 0466 169 997</p><p><br /></p><p>www.hrc.act.gov.au</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>From: Wendell Charles NeSmith [mailto:wendell@nesmith.net]</p><p>Sent: Friday, 14 September 2012 5:37 PM</p><p>To: Human Rights</p><p>Subject: Mental Health</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>Our mental health systems are flawed at their core.</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>Here is my complaint:</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>www.nesmith.net/articles/the-psychiatric-model</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>Wendell Charles NeSmith (You will hear that name for the rest of your life so please don't overlook this)</p><p><br /></p><p>---------- Forwarded message ----------</p><p>From: Ombudsman <Ombudsman@ombudsman.gov.au></p><p>Date: Fri, Sep 14, 2012 at 4:53 PM</p><p>Subject: Ombudsman's response - Our ref: 2012-117556 [SEC=UNOFFICIAL]</p><p>To: "wendell@nesmith.net" <wendell@nesmith.net></p><p><br /></p><p>Our ref: 2012-117556</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>Dear Sir</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>Thank you for your email of 13 September 2012 in which you complain about health services in the Australian Capital Territory (ACT).</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>We cannot help you with this matter. The ACT Ombudsmanâ€™s office investigates complaints about the actions of ACT Government agencies. However, under our legislation we cannot investigate matters relating to a small number of these agencies, including ACT Health. Therefore we cannot investigate your complaint.</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>The Heath Services Commissioner can consider investigating complaints about ACT Health. You may wish to contact them to see if they can help. The contact details are:</p><p><br /></p><p>Â </p><p><br /></p><p>Postal:Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Â  Health Ser